<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application><acronym>GNOME</acronym> Games</application></title>

<para>Installez <application><acronym>GNOME</acronym> Games</application> en lançant les commandes
suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=$GNOME_PREFIX --localstatedir=/var/lib \
--sysconfdir=/etc/gnome &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

